name: Getting in Group Limited
tag_list: personal-statement, gcse-revision, a-level-revision, university-choices, university-courses, students
overview: Getting-in.com provides a one-stop shop for all the needs of a student preparing for university life, from their initial choice of university and course through to the process of writing a personal statement and finally their preparation for those all-important final exams. A typical student visiting to Getting-in.com at this time will find a comprehensive range of information to help them as they decide which course and which university will be right for them. The site offers university guides for all of the UK’s main universities, which cover not just essential information on facilities and academic quality but also present the inside track on what life is really like there and important considerations such as how the social scene of campus universities varies from their city-centre counterparts. Alongside a thorough course search feature offering information on course content and entrance requirements, Getting-in.com provides students with all they need to make an informed decision on their choice of university and course. Getting-in.com is every bit as helpful in preparing students for the next step of the university application process, namely giving ucas advice. Getting-in.com also offers a fantastic range of revision guides to help students as exam time approaches
